<p><a href="#_ftnref2" name="_ftn2">[2]</a> Ibid.</p>
<p><a href="#_ftnref3" name="_ftn3">[3]</a> Edwards to Dave Heath, Aug. 29, 1963, Institutional Archives, Art Institute of Chicago.</p>
